OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day with plenty of sunshine
OL,7,Fthis evening, then staying dry and
OL,8,Fclear overnight. Some mist and fog
OL,9,Fpatches are likely to form in some
OL,10,Fprone rural spots during the early
OL,11,Fhours. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FEarly morning mist and fog
OL,14,Fpatches quickly clearing to leave a
OL,15,Ffine and very warm, locally hot day,
OL,16,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Light winds
OL,17,Fthroughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
